OL,7,FLivestreaming of most evidence will be
OL,8,Fthe "default option" for the upcoming
OL,9,FNottingham inquiry, the chairwoman for
OL,10,Fthe probe has said.
OL,12,FValdo Calocane killed University of
OL,13,FNottingham students Barnaby Webber and
OL,14,FGrace O'Malley-Kumar, both 19, and
OL,15,Fcaretaker Ian Coates, 65, before
OL,16,Fattempting to kill three other people
OL,17,Fin the city in June 2023.
