OL,5,Cchairwoman
OL,7,FThe public inquiry, chaired by senior
OL,8,Fretired judge Deborah Taylor, is
OL,9,Fexpected to begin substantive hearings
OL,10,Finto the attacks on February 23 2026,
OL,11,Fand aims to report back within two
OL,12,Fyears.
OL,14,FAt the first preliminary hearing on
OL,15,FNovember 7th, Ms Taylor received
OL,16,Fsubmissions on behalf of survivors and
OL,17,Fpeople bereaved by the attacks, as
OL,18,Fwell as multiple public bodies and the
OL,19,Fmedia over whether there should be
OL,20,Flivestream access to the proceedings
OL,21,Fand whether they should be broadcast.
