OL,4,Cevidence to be 'default option',
OL,5,Cchairwoman
OL,7,FIn a ruling published on Wednesday,
OL,8,Fthe chairwoman said livestreaming will
OL,9,Fbe the "default option" for evidence,
OL,10,Fthough some sensitive material will
OL,11,Fnot be livestreamed.
OL,13,FMs Taylor said: "Whilst the wide
OL,14,Fpublic interest in these proceedings
OL,15,Fis satisfied by a livestream, equally,
OL,16,Fthere is a public interest in
OL,17,Fretaining the option of no
OL,18,Flivestreaming for some sensitive
OL,19,Fmaterial and evidence."
