OL,7,FEvidence that is livestreamed can also
OL,8,Fbe broadcast, Ms Taylor ruled.
OL,10,FDuring the preliminary hearing, Tim
OL,11,FMoloney KC, on behalf of the bereaved
OL,12,Ffamilies, said there could be "public
OL,13,Fsurprise and disappointment" if there
OL,14,Fwas no remote way to observe the
OL,15,Finquiry ` which will take place in
OL,16,FLondon.
