OL,4,Cevidence to be 'default option',
OL,5,Cchairwoman
OL,7,FHe said: "There is a great public
OL,8,Finterest in these proceedings which
OL,9,Fcould be satisfied by a livestream,
OL,10,Fbut there is also a public interest in
OL,11,Fensuring that material that should not
OL,12,Fbe livestreamed is not livestreamed.
OL,14,F"Where it is possible to broadcast
OL,15,Fevidence and have the public make
OL,16,Ftheir own mind up, we say the public
OL,17,Fshould be able to see that evidence."
