OL,7,FCalocane was sentenced to an
OL,8,Findefinite hospital order in January
OL,9,F2024 after admitting manslaughter by
OL,10,Fdiminished responsibility and
OL,11,Fattempted murder.
OL,13,FThe Ministry of Justice previously
OL,14,Fsaid the management of Calocane's risk
OL,15,Fto others in the lead-up to the
OL,16,Fattacks, and public servants accessing
OL,17,Finformation without authorisation,
OL,18,Fwill form part of the inquiry.
